physical_examinations.relevant_findings: Tanner stage I breasts, Tanner stage IV pubic hair, normal external female genitalia, normal vaginal introitus, hypoplastic uterus, no palpable gonads. Karyotype: 46,XY.

Physiologically normal with Tanner stage V breasts and sparse pubic hair. Normal external genitalia and normal vaginal introitus. Pelvic examination revealed a retroverted uterus with no adnexal masses. Karyotype: 46,XY.
Normal breast development and menstruation until menopause at age 49, after which hormone replacement therapy was given for 2 years.
